### 4. Criar Pet (Coelho)
POST {{baseUrl}}/pets
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Tambor",
  "type": "rabbit",
  "breed": "Angorá",
  "gender": "male",
  "birthDate": "2022-01-15",
