### 5. Listar Todos os Pets
GET {{baseUrl}}/pets
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Buscar Pet por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/pets/{{petId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Buscar Pets por Customer
GET {{baseUrl}}/pets/customer/{{customerId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Atualizar Pet (Peso)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/pets/{{petId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "weight": 27.5
}

### 9. Atualizar Pet (Completo)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/pets/{{petId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Rex Jr",
  "weight": 28.0,
  "notes": "Atualizando informações após consulta veterinária"
}

### 10. Deletar Pet
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/pets/{{petId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

